            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Hd1e108">Rubrica 4</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De munere diuino</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>
               ¶ De munere diuino. Rubrica. 4.
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e119">
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>PSalmista. Psalmus 36. </ref>
                  <quote <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>Apud dominum
                  <lb ed="#V" n="60"/> gressus hominis dirigentur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e131"> /
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e133"> 83
               <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>psalmus </ref> <quote Gratiam et gloriam dabit domi
                  <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>nus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e142"> /
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e144"> 117 psalmus. </ref> <quote Lapidem quem reproba
                  <lb ed="#V" n="63" break="no"/>uerunt edificantes: hic factus est in caput an
                  <lb ed="#V" n="64" break="no"/>guli. A domino factum est istud: hoc est mi
                  <lb ed="#V" n="65" break="no"/>rabile in oculis nostris. Hec est dies quam
                  <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>fecit dominus: exultemus et letemur in ea. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e156">
               <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e160">/ 147 psalmus. </ref> <quote Nisi dominus custodierit ciui
                  <lb ed="#V" n="68" break="no"/>tatem: frustra vigilat qui custodit eam.
                  <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>Dominus dat escam vniuerse carni. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e168"> /
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e170"> 166 
                  <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>psalmus. </ref> <quote Dominus dat escam esurientibus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e176">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e180">¶ Salomon in prouerbiis. c. 3. </ref> <quote habe fidu
                  <lb ed="#V" n="72" break="no"/>ciam in domino ex toto corde: et ne initaris pru
                  <lb ed="#V" n="73" break="no"/>dentie tue: in omnibus viis tuis cogita illum
                  <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>et ipse diriget gressus tuos. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e190"> /
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e192"> 16. c. </ref> <quote Cor ho
                  <lb ed="#V" n="75" break="no"/>minis disponet viam suam: sed domini est
                  <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>dirigere gressus eius. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e200"> /
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e202"> A domino diriguntur
                  <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>gressus viri: quis autem hominum intellige
                  <lb ed="#V" n="78" break="no"/>re potest viam suam. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e211"> /
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e213"> 21. c. </ref> <quote Cor regis in
                  <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>manu domini: quocumque voluerit inclinabit illud </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e219">
               <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e223">¶ Paralipomenon: lib. 2. c. 25. </ref> <quote Dei est adiu
                  <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>uare et in figura vertere. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e229">
               <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e233">¶ Ioannes in euangelio. c. 6. </ref> <quote  Ait iesus: Ne
                  <lb ed="#V" n="83" breal="no"/>mo potest venire ad me: nisi pater qui mi
                  <lb ed="#V" n="84" break="no"/>sit me traxerit eum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e241"> /
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e243"> 14. c. </ref> <quote Nemo venit ad
                  <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>patrem nisi per me. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e249">
               <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e253">¶ Lucas in actibus apostolorum. c. 8. </ref> <quote Cum vi
                  <lb ed="#V" n="87" break="no"/>disset simon magus quia per impositionem
                  <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>manus apostolorum daretur spiritus sanctus:
                  <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>obtulit eis pecuniam dicens: date mihi hanc
                  <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>potestatem: vt cuicumque imposuero manus: <!--26.xml-->
                  <pb ed="#V" n="2-r"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>accipiat spirtum sanctum. Petrus autem di
                  <lb ed="#V" n="2" break="no"/>xit ad eum pecunia tua si t tecum in perditionem
                  <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>quoniam donum dei existimasti pecunia possideri. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e278">
               <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e282">¶ Iacobus apostolus epistola vnica. c. i. </ref> <quote Omne da
                  <lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>tum optimum et omne donum perfectum desursum
                  <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>est: descendens a patre luminum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e291"> /
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e293"> 3 cap. </ref>  <quote
                  <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>Que desursum est sapientia: primum quidem
                  <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>pudica est: deinde pacifica: modesta: suadi
                  <lb ed="#V" n="9" break="no"/>bilis: bonis consentiens: plena minsericordia:
                  <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>et fructibus bonis iudicans sine simulatione. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e305">
               <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e309">¶ Paulus apostolus epistola prima ad corinth.
                  <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>ca. 15 Gratia dei sum id quod sum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e315"> /
              ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e317"> Idem
               <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>epistola ad ephesios. ca. 2. </ref> <quote Gratia estis sal
                  <lb ed="#V" n="14" break="no"/>uati per sidem: et hoc non ex vobis. Dei do
                  <lb ed="#V" n="15" break="no" />num est non ex operibus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e327"> /
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e329"> Idem episto
               <lb ed="#V" n="16" break="no"/>la. 2. ad corinthios. c. 3. </ref> <quote Sufficientia nostra
                  <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>ex deo est. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e337"> /
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e339"> Idem epistola ad hebreos. c. 4. </ref> <quote
                  <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>Adeamus cum fiducia ad thronum gratie: vt
                  <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>minsericordiam consequamur: et gratiam inueni
                  <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>amus in auxilio opportuno. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e349">
               <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e353">¶ Augustinus in epigramatibus prosperi: </ref> <quote 
                  <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>ca. 27. Nemo est tam eruditus: nemo tam
                  <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>doctus qui superna illustratione non egeat. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e362">
               <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e366">¶ Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 9. ca. 24 </ref> <quote Deo
                  <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>auctore omnia prosperantur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e372"> /
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e374"> 25. c. et fi. </ref> <quote Ad
                  <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>omnia redditur habilis quem imbuit doctri
                  <lb ed="#V" n="27" break="no"/>na celestis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e382"> /
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e384"> Libro. 10. c. 1. </ref> <quote Deus conseuit
                  <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>casus asperos in prospera commutare. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e390"> /
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e392"> 31 
                  <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>c. </ref> <quote Omnis prouectus ad deitatis est munera
                  <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>referendus: nec aliquid constat esse bonum:
                  <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>nisi quod ab ipso dignoscitur esse collatum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-d1e402">
               <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>
               ><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d1e792-Qd1e406"> ¶ Gualterius de castellione libro. 2. </ref> <quote Parcite
                  <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>victores ingrati viuere summo victori vi
                  <lb ed="#V" n="34" break="no"/>res: sceptrum diadema triumphus: diuiti
                  <lb ed="#V" n="35" break="no"/>as dare qui potuit auferre valebit. </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
